# Dockerfile build context lives at libsdl3-sunxifb/build/. The Dockerfile
# fetches the toolchain via curl at build time (not COPY) so we keep this
# context tiny. Defensive ignores below in case anyone later drops large
# files (toolchain tarball, intermediate test outputs) next to the
# Dockerfile and inflates the build context unnoticed.

# Toolchain tarballs — fetched in-Dockerfile, must not be here.
*.tar.xz
*.tar.gz
*.tar.bz2
*.tgz

# Cached/extracted toolchain trees — must not bleed into the image.
arm-*/
gcc-arm-*/

# Test outputs / scratch
*.elf
*.a
*.o
*.so
*.so.*
hello
hello.c

# Editor / OS noise
.*.swp
.DS_Store
*~
